{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change our electoral system to Proportional Representation for true democracy",
        "additional_details": "For far too long, balance of power has been held just between the Conservative & Labour parties. The British Parliament should directly reflect the votes of the British people - smaller parties deserve the representation of their actual votes and we, the people, need true progressive democracy.  Maybe then, we can once again trust the people running the country.",
        "background": "Please repeal First Past the Post and install a system which truly reflects the will of the people - surely PR, where votes = seats nationally rather than just the most popular candidate of a specific local area, is the only truly democratic way forward.",
